        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated by
        reference.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section density="compact" heading="Eligibility">
      <p>
        You must be at least 18 years of age, or the age of majority in
        your jurisdiction (whichever is greater), to use the Site. If
        you use the Site on behalf of an organization, you represent
        that you have authority to bind that organization to these
        Terms, and "you" refers to both you individually and that
        organization.
