        or authentication measures; (iii) reverse engineer, decompile,
        or otherwise attempt to derive the source code of any software
        delivered through the Site; (iv) interfere with or disrupt the
        Site, its servers, or networks connected to it; (v) use the
        Site to transmit malicious code, viruses, or harmful content;
        (vi) impersonate any person or misrepresent your affiliation
        with any person or entity; or (vii) use the Site to violate any
        applicable law or third-party right.
      </p>
    </Section>

